requests.description:

requests.name: Update your password
requests.description:
Update your API password. All future requests to /v3/tokens must use the new password to properly authenticate.

New API passwords have several requirements:

* Must be at least 6 characters long
* Must contain a letter, a number, and a special character
* Must not contain or be similar to your registered email or Quovo API username
